features: PACKING CUBES MAKE TRAVEL EASIER-Compression cubes help you with packaging your clothes for upcoming trips by compressing the air out of them. Save up to 30% more space in your suitcase!
LUGGAGE ORGANIZER- Keep different outfits in separate compression cubes and always be ready for what’s next! Easily pack away clothing like raincoats/heavier jackets that are not used as often.

HOW MUCH DOES EXTRA LARGE SET HOLD?- Extra Large packing cube holds approx 3 Mens Large Tshirts, Large puffy jacket, 2 long sleeve large shirts, one pair jeans, one pair mens pants. Large compression cube holds 2 mens tshirts, 1 pair mens pants, and 2 long sleeve shirts. Small compression cube holds about 8 womens shirts. Tube cube holds electronics, toiletries, underwear or swimsuits. Laundry bag is great for dirty clothes or shoes.

USE EXPANDED OR COMPRESSED- Use these like normal packing cubes when you need to pack more. Packing less? Use the compression zipper to save even more space! Extra Large Dimensions Compressed size: 15.7x11x4in Large Dimensions Compressed size: 14x10x1in Expanded Size: 14x10x4in Small Dimensions Compressed size 10x7x1in Expanded Size: 10x7x4in

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect pricing, slightly imperfect coloration
reviews.reviewText: These are perfect for traveling! Very lightweight but strong zippers for compression. I couldn't pass up the price when I saw these and knew to expect some imperfections and I'm shocked at how little there is to notice. There are two semi circle of reddish/pink and a slight blue watercolor spot on two of the bags but other then that they were off perfect quality. No structural defects, no odd or bad smells. They are first quality and a steal if you're ordering them for $25. I only actually need 3 of the bags but at this price it was silly to not order the entire set

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 2, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Large compression cubes at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: After 25 years, we decided to replace our luggage set (we obviously haven’t been big travelers, mostly trips by car, maybe only a dozen flights during that time). I went with a highly rated brand of luggage with spinner wheels and retractable handle (SO MUCH EASIER than our previous luggage). I knew that meant less packable space, so I started researching compression packing cubes. We’re a family of five, so I see the possible need for more than one set. There are a number of name brands that different reviewers mention/recommend, so I at least had a selection to look at. I kept coming back to Tripped.Then I stumbled across a discounted listing for Tripped XL compression packing cube 6-piece set (due to light staining). At a reduced price for a recommended brand, I couldn’t pass it up. It arrived quickly and I played with it for a bit. I washed all 6 pieces in cold water on a gentle cycle. I can’t find any staining now!This set on Tripped’s website suggests use in a checked bag. I missed that before ordering. I was just thinking about my chronic overpacking ways when looking at cube sets. (And delighted with a discounted price!)My set includes (per listing):1 laundry/shoe bag1 slim tube2 XL compression cubes—16x121 med. compression cube—14x10***1 small compression cube—10x7***I’ve read some descriptions that don’t list distinct measurements for the medium versus the large bag. This listing says this 14x10 is a medium bag. If I order another set that includes a “large” bag, will its measurements also be 14x10? I’m not certain.I know a review is more helpful after real-world use. Since I read and watched video reviews recommending these compression cubes, I am not concerned about longevity. I’m sure they’ll be great!

reviews.reviewTitle: Les tuve fé y valió la pena
reviews.reviewText: Tengo meses buscando un buen kit de cubos de compresión para viaje ya que cada vez es menos el peso o tamaño que te dejan llevar en la maleta, y cuando menos lo esperé, me topé con estos de Tripped que en general tienen muy buenas reviews en sus sets alternos (aunque mas caros). Estos tienen descuento únicamente por que están algo manchados, cosa que a menos que tengan vision 20/20 y luz brillante encima de ustedes todo el tiempo, es casi imposible de distinguir. Me encantaron, espero duren muchos años.
I love the product, design and the quality. This is exactly what I'm looking for and i also bought a matching toiletries bag 😉💕

reviews.reviewTitle: Organized my holiday clothes day by day
reviews.reviewText: I used this compression luggage for my trip to Iceland for the first time. I used them in my carry-on as well as my suitcase. It kept me organized and on track with challenging wintery weather of Iceland . Lightweight, durable, and easy. Everyone should travel this way.
Tenía un poco de escepticismo sobre ellas, son las primeros organizadores que compro y estoy sorprendido por la organización y espacio que proporcionan
